        li.fade-in.delay-200ms
          span.time 2010
          span.dot: img src="/images/policies_image/food_safely/fs1_2.png"
          .timeline-content: p 知名豆乾引發肉毒桿菌中毒事件、紅茶冰含致癌原料
        li.fade-in.delay-400ms
          span.time 2011
          span.dot: img src="/images/policies_image/food_safely/fs1_3.png"
          .timeline-content: p 塑化劑飲料
        li.fade-in.delay-600ms
          span.time 2012
          span.dot: img src="/images/policies_image/food_safely/fs1_4.png"
          .timeline-content: p 瘦肉精牛肉
        li.fade-in.delay-800ms
